  "slug": "junior-squash-event-fundraiser-raffle",
  "title": "Support Junior Squash in Edmonton Raffle",
  "excerpt": "UPDATE FROM JULIE July 14th 2017: Congratulations to our winners! Wine/Liquor Basket &#8211; Garth Laturnus Beer Basket &#8211; Stephen Visser Beer Basket &#8211; Michael Burgess We raised $1550 in cash, and another $200 in gift cards were donated. Many thanks to everyone who donated. Regards, Julie ________________ Growing the game of squash is one &#8230; Read more",
  "content": "<div>UPDATE FROM JULIE July 14th 2017:</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Congratulations to our winners!</div>\n<div></div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55258\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55264\">Wine/Liquor Basket &#8211; Garth Laturnus</span></div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55265\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55264\">Beer Basket &#8211; Stephen Visser</span></div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55275\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55264\">Beer Basket &#8211; Michael Burgess</span></div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55279\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55264\"> </span></div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55374\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55264\">We raised $1550 in cash, and another $200 in gift cards were donated.<br />\n</span></div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55425\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55443\">Many thanks to everyone who donated.</span></div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55453\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55443\">Regards,</span></div>\n<div id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55458\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1499957565025_55443\">Julie</span></div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>________________</div>\n<div>Growing the game of squash is one of the Edmonton Squash Club&#8217;s most important mandates. And what better way to do that than by hosting the Edmonton Junior Squash Events which have come to be among the busiest and most fun days each year at the club!</div>\n<div></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5737\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5738\">As many of you know, club-pro Julie Multamaki and Heather Sanregret organise two Jr Squash events each year for our young developing squash players in Edmonton and area. These one-day events offer beginner and developmental players from 5-18 yrs of age, an opportunity to compete in a fun environment with children of similar abilities (not by age group or sex), with modified balls appropriate for their ability levels. Each child receives 3-4 matches, and they are encouraged to learn the rules, plus mark and referee the ensuing match. (We have adult volunteers to help young and beginner kids with the refereeing and marking).<br id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5739\" /></span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5740\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5741\"> </span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5743\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5744\">Every child goes home with a prize &#8211; we do not give out prizes for 1st-3rd, as this is a developmental event, and participation is more important at this stage. That being said, our annual fundraising campaign is about garnering financial support from our squash playing community. We are asking for squash players to please consider donating either a $20 gift card or $20 cash towards supporting the prizes for our 2 events this coming season. The first event each season is held at the Royal Glenora Club in October, and the 2nd event is hosted by the Edmonton Squash Club in April.<br id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5745\" /></span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5746\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5747\"> </span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5749\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5750\">Gift cards that kids love include (but are not limited to) Chapters/Indigo; i-Tunes; Best Buy; Netflix; Cineplex Odeon Movie Passes; Lulu Lemon; Google Play; X-Box; Sportchek; and Sweet Spot. We&#8217;ll also gladly take new grips, bags and racquets etc. that have been hanging around your closet for years!<br id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5751\" /></span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5752\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5753\"> </span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5755\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5756\">In return for your $20 donation, we will give you 3 draw tickets to be used in our 3 fabulous summer beverage draws &#8211;  products have been generously donated by WWSE, George <span class=\"lG\">Multamaki</span>, Mark Anthony Wines, Lanigan &amp; Edwards Wine Merchants, Labatt&#8217;s, and Sleeman&#8217;s.  We have 2 beer baskets and one wine/liquor basket up for grabs.</span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5757\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5758\"> </span></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"fl-builder-content fl-builder-content-1415 fl-builder-template fl-builder-row-template fl-builder-global-templates-locked\" data-post-id=\"1415\"><div class=\"fl-row fl-row-fixed-width fl-row-bg-none fl-node-59642a1d33961 fl-row-default-height fl-row-align-center\" data-node=\"59642a1d33961\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-row-content-wrap\">\n\t\t<div class=\"uabb-row-separator uabb-top-row-separator\" >\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-row-content fl-row-fixed-width fl-node-content\">\n\t\t\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-59642a1d338a1\" data-node=\"59642a1d338a1\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-59642a1d338e3 fl-col-bg-color\" data-node=\"59642a1d338e3\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\"><div class=\"fl-module fl-module-uabb-numbers fl-node-59642a1d33923\" data-node=\"59642a1d33923\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"uabb-module-content uabb-number uabb-number-none-above-title uabb-number-circle\" role=\"group\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Counter module showing numbers\">\n\t<div class=\"uabb-number-circle-container\">\t\n\t\t<div class=\"uabb-number-text\">\n\t\t<span class=\"uabb-number-before-text\">Total Money Collected</span><h2 class=\"uabb-number-string\">$<span class=\"uabb-number-int\">0</span></h2><span class=\"uabb-number-after-text\">We hope to raise $1,500 by July 13th</span>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"svg-container\"><svg class=\"svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 300 300\" version=\"1.1\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n\t\t\t<circle class=\"uabb-bar-bg\" r=\"145\" cx=\"150\" cy=\"150\" fill=\"transparent\" stroke-dasharray=\"911.06\" stroke-dashoffset=\"0\"></circle>\n\t\t\t<circle class=\"uabb-bar\" r=\"145\" cx=\"150\" cy=\"150\" fill=\"transparent\" stroke-dasharray=\"911.06\" stroke-dashoffset=\"911.06\" transform=\"rotate(-90.1 150 150)\"></circle>\n\t\t</svg></div>\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"uabb-js-breakpoint\" style=\"display: none;\"></div></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"> <a href=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/WineBasket1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1407\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/WineBasket1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"506\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/WineBasket1.jpg 600w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/WineBasket1-300x253.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/WineBasket1-20x17.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket2a.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1408\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"501\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket2a.jpg 600w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket2a-300x251.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket2a-20x17.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1409\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket1.jpg 600w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket1-225x300.jpg 225w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/BeerBasket1-15x20.jpg 15w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5760\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5761\">Heather and/or Julie will be at the ESC Summer League each Tuesday &amp; Thursday, from June 27 &#8211; July 13, 2017 to collect gift cards/donations, and to distribute draw tickets. All draws will be made on Thursday, July 13th at 8:30pm. If you are not in attendance that evening, we will contact you and arrange to get your prize to you!<br id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5762\" /></span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5763\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5764\"> </span></div>\n<div id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5766\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"m_9120999496892802123yiv3063698471yui_3_16_0_ym19_1_1498233208962_5767\">If you have any questions about this fundraiser or our EJSE&#8217;s please do not hesitate to contact Julie at <a href=\"mailto:edmontonjrsquashevents@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">edmontonjrsquashevents@gmail.<wbr />com</a></span></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"></div>\n</div>\n",
